node.text:
Happy Labor Day!! 🇺🇸🎉 hope everyone enjoyed the weekend and celebrated a little! What did y’all do?
Also apparently the leaner I get, the taller I look🤣 so I guess you could say the shred is starting to get serious 🤓
PS don’t forget all apparel & training is 40% OFF with code “LDW40”! Ends tonight 👀 #linkinbio

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Carriejune Anne Bowlby on September 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Low quality pic, high quality workout 💪🏼🤓 goal the past few weeks has been to shred down while maintaining the muscle I was building all winter-summer🤯 longest “bulk” ever lol
Happy Labor Day weekend!! Any fun plans?
Also new YouTube vid going up as soon as it’s finished uploading…🙇🏼‍♀️😂

node.text:
It’s not the goal achieved that matters as much as who you become on the way to achieving it 💪🏼
Who else started the weekend strong? Minibeast clients I see you👀😂🖤

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Carriejune Anne Bowlby on August 25, 2021 tagging @aboutit, @dont, @even, @christinemelanie_, @jk, and @think. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: Let me tell ya bout my best frannn😍 HAPPY BIRTHDAY🎂🎉 to my childhood partner in crime since day 1🤣 until forever! People pray for a friend like you but God blessed me with you as my sister🙏🏼 I hope everyone has someone in their lives who is just as supportive, good hearted, caring, funny and pure as you are Chrissy🥰 @christinemelanie_ I LOVE YOU!

node.text:
Do what you love but call it work 💪🏼
My Fall Challenge gets sent out in 2 DAYS! Link in bio to see some of my client transformations and join us! Limited spots 👀
Details:
•My Coaching for 8 weeks 
•5 workout programs (At Home and Gym options)
-Shred fat, Gain muscle, or Recomp *combo of the 2*
•Custom cals / macros for each individual 🤯
•Example diets with a ton of variety
•Private Facebook support group
*NEW Athletic Trainer on staff to help with exercise modifications for those with injuries, etc.
*NEW Nutritionist on staff to modify your diet/meal plan to your needs, dietary restrictions, etc.
*NEW workout demo videos for all exercises with a brand new easy format
•Chance to win $1000 in cash, Minibeast Apparel and more
•Equally Effective for Men and Women
...and SO MUCH MORE!
